            <p class="is-txt-white">Donec pulvinar eros non nunc porta hendrerit. Morbi aliquet malesuada elit, ut pharetra nulla ornare eu. Morbi dapibus quis urna at bibendum. Nunc pharetra lacus et massa gravida, in accumsan lorem iaculis.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="app__button d-none d-lg-block">
            <%= link_to "Comece agora", "#", class: "btn btn-md btn-white is-txt-medium", id: "focus-formExchange" %>
          </div>
          <div class="app__credits d-none d-lg-block">
            <p class="is-txt-green-dark">Desenvolvido por <%= link_to 'Felipe Marcon', '#', class:"is-txt-white" %> no Bootcamp da OneBitCode.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col col-sm-12 col-md-8 offset-md-2 col-lg-6 offset-lg-0 px-lg-0 col-xl-7">
        <div class="app__col app__col--right">
          <div class="app__card">
            <div class="app__card--head">
              <h1 class="is-txt-medium is-txt-green-light">Simule a sua convers√£o</h1>
